<w canon="pimiy" class="ni" gcat="0sNI" sgloss="fat" stem="pimiy" suffix="0">pimiy</w>
.</q>
<gloss>When he came into the tent, “Old woman, give me some fat.”</gloss>
</seg>
</p>

<p n="14">

<seg n="14.1">
<w canon="miyik" class="vta" gcat="3o3sTA" sgloss="give_to" stem="miy" suffix="-ik">miyik</w>
<w canon="pimiy" class="ni" gcat="0sNI" sgloss="fat" stem="pimiy" suffix="0">pimiy</w>
.
<gloss>She gave him fat.</gloss>
</seg>

<seg n="14.2">
