<w canon="êkota" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="there" stem="êkota">êkotah</w>
<w canon="pimiy" class="ni" gcat="0sNI" sgloss="fat" stem="pimiy" suffix="0">pimiy</w>
.
<gloss>Then he put the poison into the fat; and into a small dish he poured the fat.</gloss>
</seg>

<seg n="14.3">
<w canon="mihcêt" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="many" stem="mihcêt">mihcêt</w>
<w canon="êkota" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="there" stem="êkota">êkotah</w>
