<w canon="pêyak" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="one" stem="pêyak">pêyak</w>
.
<gloss>Presently he saw a wolf.</gloss>
</seg>
</p>

<p n="17">

<seg n="17.1">
<q>
<w canon="â" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="ah" stem="â">âh</w>
,
<w canon="nisîm" class="nda" gcat="3sNDAof1s" prefix="1" sgloss="younger_sib" stem="sîm" suffix="0">nisîm</w>
,
<w canon="âstam" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="come_here" stem="âstam">âstam</w>
!</q>
-
<w canon="ôhi" class="dem" gcat="3oDEM" sgloss="this" stem="awa" suffix="-3o">ôhi</w>
<w canon="mahîhkana" class="na" gcat="3oNA" sgloss="wolf" stem="mahîhkan" suffix="-a">mahîhkanah</w>
.
<gloss>“Hey, brother, come here!”  to that wolf.</gloss>
</seg>
</p>

<p n="18">

<seg n="18.1">
<q>
<w canon="â" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="ah" stem="â">â</w>
,
<w canon="namôya" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="not" stem="namôya">namôya</w>
!</q>
<w canon="itwêw" class="vai" gcat="3sAI" sgloss="say" stem="itwê" suffix="-w">itwêw</w>
<w canon="mahîhkan" class="na" gcat="3sNA" sgloss="wolf" stem="mahîhkan" suffix="0">mahîhkan</w>
,
<q>
<w canon="ê" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="well" stem="â">ê</w>
,
<w canon="kiwî-nipahin" class="vta" gcat="2s1sTA" prefix="2" preverbs="wî|will" sgloss="kill" stem="nipah" suffix="-in">kiwîh-nipahin</w>
<w canon="osâm" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="because" stem="osâm">osâm</w>
!</q>
<gloss>“Oh dear, no!” said the wolf; “Why, you want to kill me!”</gloss>
</seg>
</p>

<p n="19">

<seg n="19.1">
<q>
<w canon="namôya" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="not" stem="namôya">namôya</w>
,
<w canon="nisîm" class="nda" gcat="3sNDAof1s" prefix="1" sgloss="younger_sib" stem="sîm" suffix="0">nisîm</w>
.
<w canon="ê-wî-masinahikêhitin" class="vta" gcat="1s2sTA" preverbs="ê|cnj wî|will" sgloss="hire" stem="masinahikêh" suffix="-itin">ê-wîh-masinahikêhitan</w>
.</q>
<gloss>“No, little brother. I want to employ you.”</gloss>
</seg>
</p>

<p n="20">

<seg n="20.1">
<q>
<w canon="tânisi" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="how" stem="tânisi">tânisi</w>
<w canon="ê-wî-isi-masinahikêhiyan" class="vta" gcat="2s1sTAcnj" preverbs="ê|cnj wî|will isi|thus" sgloss="hire" stem="masinahikêh" suffix="-iyan">ê-wîh-isi-masinahikêhiyan</w>
.</q>
<gloss>“How do you want to employ me?”</gloss>
</seg>
</p>

<p n="21">

<seg n="21.1">
<q rend="PRE 1 POST0">
<w canon="ê-wî-atoskahitân" class="vta" gcat="1s2sTAcnj" preverbs="ê|cnj wî|will" sgloss="make_work" stem="atoskah" suffix="-itân">ê-wîh-atoskahitân</w>
<w canon="ka-papâ-nitomacik" class="vta" gcat="2s3pTAcnj" preverbs="ka|will papâ|around" sgloss="call" stem="nitom" suffix="-acik">ka-papâ-ntomacik</w>
<w canon="mahîhkanak" class="na" gcat="3pNA" sgloss="wolf" stem="mahîhkan" suffix="-ak">mahîhkanak</w>
<w canon="mîna" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="also" stem="mîna">mîna</w>
<w canon="mahkêsîsak" class="na" gcat="3pNA" sgloss="Fox" stem="mahkêsîs" suffix="-ak">mahkêsîsak</w>
,
<w canon="kahkiyaw" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="every" stem="kahkiyaw">kahkiyaw</w>
<w canon="kâ-miyosicik" class="vai" gcat="3pAIcnj" preverbs="kâ|cnj" sgloss="be_good" stem="miyosi" suffix="-cik">kâ-miyosicik</w>
<w canon="mahkêsîsak" class="na" gcat="3pNA" sgloss="Fox" stem="mahkêsîs" suffix="-ak">mahkêsîsak</w>
.</q>
<gloss>“I want to give you the work of going round and summoning the wolves and foxes, all the good-looking foxes.</gloss>
</seg>

<seg n="21.2">
<q rend="PRE 0 POST1">
<w canon="ôta" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="here" stem="ôta">ôtah</w>
<w canon="nika-apin" class="vai" gcat="1sAI" prefix="1" preverbs="ka|will" sgloss="sit" stem="api" suffix="-n">nik-âpin</w>
<w canon="ispatinâhk" class="ni" gcat="0locNI" sgloss="hill" stem="ispatinâw" suffix="-ihk">ispatinâhk</w>
,
<w canon="ê-wî-kakêskimitakok" class="vta" gcat="1s2pTAcnj" preverbs="ê|cnj wî|will" sgloss="counsel" stem="kakêskim" suffix="-itakok">ê-wîh-kakêskimitakok</w>
,
<w canon="ê-miywâsihk" class="vii" gcat="0sIIcnj" preverbs="ê|cnj" sgloss="be_good" stem="miywâsin" suffix="-k">ê-miywâsihk</w>
<w canon="âcimôwin" class="ni" gcat="0sNI" sgloss="story" stem="âcimowin" suffix="0">âcimôwin</w>
<w canon="ka-wîhtamâtakok" class="vta" gcat="1s2pTAcnj" preverbs="ka|will" sgloss="tell_about" stem="wîhtamaw" suffix="-itakok">ka-wîhtamâtakok</w>
.</q>
<gloss>I shall be sitting here on this knoll, ready to preach to you, to tell you good tidings.”</gloss>
</seg>
</p>

<p n="22">

<seg n="22.1">
<w canon="êkwa" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="then" stem="êkwa">êkwah</w>
<w canon="tâpwê" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="truly" stem="tâpwê">tâpwê</w>
<w canon="awa" class="dem" gcat="3sDEM" sgloss="this" stem="awa">awa</w>
<w canon="mahîhkan" class="na" gcat="3sNA" sgloss="wolf" stem="mahîhkan" suffix="0">mahîhkan</w>
<w canon="sipwêhtêw" class="vai" gcat="3sAI" sgloss="leave" stem="sipwêhtê" suffix="-w">sipwêhtêw</w>
,
<w canon="ê-nitomât" class="vta" gcat="3s3oTAcnj" preverbs="ê|cnj" sgloss="call" stem="nitom" suffix="-ât">ê-nitomât</w>
<w canon="mahîhkana" class="na" gcat="3oNA" sgloss="wolf" stem="mahîhkan" suffix="-a">mahîhkanah</w>
<w canon="mîna" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="also" stem="mîna">mîna</w>
<w canon="mahkêsîsa" class="na" gcat="3oNA" sgloss="Fox" stem="mahkêsîs" suffix="-a">mahkêsîsah</w>
.
<gloss>So that wolf went off to call the wolves and foxes.</gloss>
</seg>

<seg n="22.2">
<w canon="tâpwê" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="truly" stem="tâpwê">tâpwê</w>
<w canon="pêtohtêwak" class="vai" gcat="3pAI" sgloss="come" stem="pêtohtê" suffix="-wak">pêtohtêwak</w>
<w canon="mihcêt" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="many" stem="mihcêt">mihcêt</w>
<w canon="mahîhkanak" class="na" gcat="3pNA" sgloss="wolf" stem="mahîhkan" suffix="-ak">mahîhkanak</w>
.
<gloss>Indeed, many wolves came.</gloss>
</seg>

<seg n="22.3">
<w canon="mitoni" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="intensively" stem="mitoni">mitoni</w>
<w canon="misiwê" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="all_over" stem="misiwê">misiwê</w>
<w canon="wâsakâm" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="around_a_circle" stem="wâsakâm">wâsakâm</w>
<w canon="apiyiwa" class="vai" gcat="3oAI" sgloss="sit" stem="api" suffix="-yiwa">apiyiwah</w>
,
<w canon="ê-wî-nitohtâkot" class="vta" gcat="3o3sTAcnj" preverbs="ê|cnj wî|will" sgloss="listen_to" stem="nitohtaw" suffix="-ikot">ê-wîh-ntohtâkot</w>
,
<w canon="tâpiskôc" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="like" stem="tâpiskôc">tâpiskôc</w>
<w canon="ayamihêwiyiniw" class="na" gcat="3sNA" sgloss="priest" stem="ayamihêwiyiniw" suffix="0">ayimihêwiyiniw</w>
<w canon="wîsahkêcâhk" class="na" gcat="3sNA" sgloss="Wisahketchahk" stem="wîsahkêcâhkw" suffix="0">wîsahkêcâhk</w>
.
<gloss>In great numbers they sat round in a circle, to listen to Wisahketchahk, exactly as if he were a missionary.</gloss>
</seg>
</p>

<p n="23">

<seg n="23.1">
<w canon="ômisi" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="thus" stem="ômisi">ômisîh</w>
<w canon="itêw" class="vta" gcat="3s3oTA" sgloss="say_to" stem="it" suffix="-êw">itêw</w>
:
<q rend="PRE 1 POST0">
<w canon="nisîmitik" class="nda" extra="vocp" gcat="3pNDAof1svoc" prefix="1" sgloss="younger_sib" stem="sîm" suffix="-VOCp">nisîmitik</w>
,
<w canon="ayamihâwin" class="ni" gcat="0sNI" sgloss="prayer" stem="ayamihâwin" suffix="0">ayamihâwin</w>
<w canon="kâ-nitohtamêk" class="vti" gcat="2pTIcnj" preverbs="kâ|cnj" sgloss="listen_to" stem="nitoht" suffix="-amêk">kâ-ntohtamêk</w>
<w canon="ta-otinamêk" class="vti" gcat="2pTIcnj" preverbs="ta|FUT" sgloss="take" stem="otin" suffix="-amêk">t-ôtinamêk</w>
;</q>
<gloss>This is what he said: “My brothers, the tidings which you hear you should accept,</gloss>
</seg>

<seg n="23.2">
<q rend="PRE 0 POST0">
<w canon="êkosi" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="thus" stem="êkosi">êkosi</w>
<w canon="êkwa" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="then" stem="êkwa">êkwah</w>
<w canon="namôya" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="not" stem="namôya">namoy</w>
<w canon="awiyak" class="pr" gcat="3sPR" sgloss="someone" stem="awiyak">âwiyak</w>
<w canon="ka-nipahikowâwak" class="vta" gcat="3p2pTA" preverbs="ka|will" sgloss="kill" stem="nipah" suffix="-ikowâwak">ka-nipahikowâwak</w>
,
<w canon="ayamihâyêko" class="vta" gcat="2p3sTAsubjunc" sgloss="speak_to" stem="ayamih" suffix="-âyêko">ayamihâyêkoh</w>
.</q>
<gloss>and then no one will ever kill you, if you take on religion.</gloss>
</seg>

<seg n="23.3">
<q rend="PRE 0 POST0">
<w canon="mâka" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="but" stem="mâka">mâka</w>
<w canon="êkâ" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="not_to" stem="êkâ">êkâh</w>
<w canon="tâpwêhtamêko" class="vti" gcat="2pTIsubjunc" sgloss="agree_with" stem="tâpwêht" suffix="-amêko">tâpwêhtamêkoh</w>
,
<w canon="ka-nipahikowâwak" class="vta" gcat="3p2pTA" preverbs="ka|will" sgloss="kill" stem="nipah" suffix="-ikowâwak">ka-nipahikowâwak</w>
.</q>
<gloss>But if you do not believe, someone will kill you.</gloss>
</seg>

<seg n="23.4">
<q rend="PRE 0 POST1">
<w canon="îh" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="lo" stem="îh">îh</w>
<w canon="ôhi" class="dem" gcat="0pDEM" sgloss="this" stem="ôma" suffix="-0p">ôhi</w>
<w canon="wâpahtamok" class="vti" gcat="2pTIimp" sgloss="see" stem="wâpaht" suffix="-amok">wâpahtamok</w>
,
<w canon="îh" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="lo" stem="îh">êh</w>
<w canon="ôhi" class="dem" gcat="0pDEM" sgloss="this" stem="ôma" suffix="-0p">ôhi</w>
!</q>
<gloss>Look upon these things, these here!”</gloss>
<note>LB original has hyphens in {îh-ôhi} and {êh-ôhi}. HCW: should be separate words.</note>
</seg>

<seg n="23.5">
<w canon="mahîhkanak" class="na" gcat="3pNA" sgloss="wolf" stem="mahîhkan" suffix="-ak">mahîhkanak</w>
<w canon="mahkêsîsak" class="na" gcat="3pNA" sgloss="Fox" stem="mahkêsîs" suffix="-ak">mahkêsîsak</w>
<w canon="ê-wâpahtahkik" class="vti" gcat="3pTIcnj" preverbs="ê|cnj" sgloss="see" stem="wâpaht" suffix="-ahkik">ê-wâpahtahkik</w>
<w canon="ôhi" class="dem" gcat="0pDEM" sgloss="this" stem="ôma" suffix="-0p">ôhi</w>
<w canon="pimiya" class="ni" gcat="0pNI" sgloss="fat" stem="pimiy" suffix="-a">pimiyah</w>
,
<q>
<w canon="hâw" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="now" stem="hâw">hâw</w>
,
<w canon="ôma" class="dem" gcat="0sDEM" sgloss="this" stem="ôma">omah</w>
<w canon="awiyak" class="pr" gcat="3sPR" sgloss="someone" stem="awiyak">awiyak</w>
<w canon="ôma" class="dem" gcat="0sDEM" sgloss="this" stem="ôma">omah</w>
<w canon="mîcici" class="vai" gcat="3sAIsubjunc" sgloss="eat" stem="mîci" suffix="-ci">mîcici</w>
<w canon="kâ-wî-saskamohak" class="vta" gcat="1s3sTAcnj" preverbs="kâ|cnj wî|will" sgloss="put_in_mouth" stem="saskamoh" suffix="-ak">kâ-wîh-saskamohak</w>
,
<w canon="kinwês" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="for_a_long_time" stem="kinwês">kinwês</w>
<w canon="ka-pimâtisiw" class="vai" gcat="3sAI" preverbs="ka|will" sgloss="live" stem="pimâtisi" suffix="-w">ka-pimâtisiw</w>
,</q>
<w canon="êkosi" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="thus" stem="êkosi">êkosi</w>
<w canon="itwêw" class="vai" gcat="3sAI" sgloss="say" stem="itwê" suffix="-w">itwêw</w>
<w canon="wîsahkêcâhk" class="na" gcat="3sNA" sgloss="Wisahketchahk" stem="wîsahkêcâhkw" suffix="0">wîsahkêcâhk</w>
.
<gloss>As the wolves and foxes looked at those pieces of fat, “Now, then, if anyone eats this which I shall place between his teeth, long will he live,” spoke Wisahketchahk.</gloss>
</seg>
</p>

<p n="24">

<seg n="24.1">
<w canon="êkwa" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="then" stem="êkwa">êkwah</w>
<w canon="kahkiyaw" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="every" stem="kahkiyaw">kahkiyaw</w>
,
<q>
<w canon="niya" class="pr" gcat="1sPR" sgloss="I" stem="niya">niya</w>
,
<w canon="niya" class="pr" gcat="1sPR" sgloss="I" stem="niya">niya</w>
!</q>
<w canon="itwêwak" class="vai" gcat="3pAI" sgloss="say" stem="itwê" suffix="-wak">itwêwak</w>
<w canon="mahîhkanak" class="na" gcat="3pNA" sgloss="wolf" stem="mahîhkan" suffix="-ak">mahîhkanak</w>
,
<w canon="ê-miywêyihtahkik" class="vti" gcat="3pTIcnj" preverbs="ê|cnj" sgloss="consider_good" stem="miywêyiht" suffix="-ahkik">êh-miywêyihtahkik</w>
<w canon="kinwês" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="for_a_long_time" stem="kinwês">kinwês</w>
<w canon="ka-pimâtisicik" class="vai" gcat="3pAIcnj" preverbs="ka|will" sgloss="live" stem="pimâtisi" suffix="-cik">ka-pimâtisicik</w>
.
<gloss>Then all the wolves cried, “I, I!” glad that they were to live long.</gloss>
</seg>
</p>

<p n="25">

<seg n="25.1">
<q>
<w canon="êkwa" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="then" stem="êkwa">êkwah</w>
<w canon="ôma" class="dem" gcat="0sDEM" sgloss="this" stem="ôma">omah</w>
,</q>
<w canon="êkwa" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="then" stem="êkwa">êkwah</w>
<w canon="miyêw" class="vta" gcat="3s3oTA" sgloss="give_to" stem="miy" suffix="-êw">miyêw</w>
<w canon="pimiy" class="ni" gcat="0sNI" sgloss="fat" stem="pimiy" suffix="0">pimiy</w>
.
<gloss>“Here you are!” and he gave them the fat.</gloss>
</seg>
</p>

<p n="26">

<seg n="26.1">
<w canon="mîciw" class="vai" gcat="3sAI" sgloss="eat" stem="mîci" suffix="-w">mîciw</w>
<w canon="awa" class="dem" gcat="3sDEM" sgloss="this" stem="awa">awa</w>
<w canon="mahîhkan" class="na" gcat="3sNA" sgloss="wolf" stem="mahîhkan" suffix="0">mahîhkan</w>
;
<w canon="êkosi" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="thus" stem="êkosi">êkosi</w>
<w canon="êkwa" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="then" stem="êkwa">êkwah</w>
<w canon="sipwêhtêw" class="vai" gcat="3sAI" sgloss="leave" stem="sipwêhtê" suffix="-w">sipwêhtêw</w>
.
<gloss>A wolf would eat it; then he would go.</gloss>
</seg>
</p>

<p n="27">

<seg n="27.1">
<w canon="pâh-pêyak" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="singly" stem="pâh-pêyak">pâh-pêyak</w>
<w canon="ê-saskamohât" class="vta" gcat="3s3oTAcnj" preverbs="ê|cnj" sgloss="put_in_mouth" stem="saskamoh" suffix="-ât">êh-saskamohât</w>
<w canon="wâsakâm" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="around_a_circle" stem="wâsakâm">wâsakâm</w>
,
<w canon="mîna" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="also" stem="mîna">mîna</w>
<w canon="mahkêsîsa" class="na" gcat="3oNA" sgloss="Fox" stem="mahkêsîs" suffix="-a">mahkêsîsah</w>
,
<w canon="kahkiyaw" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="every" stem="kahkiyaw">kahkiyaw</w>
<w canon="mêstinam" class="vti" gcat="3sTI" sgloss="use_up" stem="mêstin" suffix="-am">mêstinam</w>
<w canon="ôma" class="dem" gcat="0sDEM" sgloss="this" stem="ôma">ômah</w>
<w canon="pimiy" class="ni" gcat="0sNI" sgloss="fat" stem="pimiy" suffix="0">pimiy</w>
.
<gloss>He placed it in their mouths, one by one, round the circle, the foxes' too, using up all the fat.</gloss>
</seg>
</p>

<p n="28">

<seg n="28.1">
<q>
<w canon="êkosi" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="thus" stem="êkosi">êkosi</w>
<w canon="kinwês" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="for_a_long_time" stem="kinwês">kinwês</w>
<w canon="ka-pimâtisinâwâw" class="vai" gcat="2pAI" preverbs="ka|will" sgloss="live" stem="pimâtisi" suffix="-nâwâw">ka-pimâtisinâwâw</w>
,
<w canon="nisîmitik" class="nda" extra="vocp" gcat="3pNDAof1svoc" prefix="1" sgloss="younger_sib" stem="sîm" suffix="-VOCp">nisîmitik</w>
,
<w canon="ôma" class="dem" gcat="0sDEM" sgloss="this" stem="ôma">oma</w>
<w canon="kâ-otinamêk" class="vti" gcat="2pTIcnj" preverbs="kâ|cnj" sgloss="take" stem="otin" suffix="-amêk">k-ôtinamêk</w>
<w canon="ayamihâwin" class="ni" gcat="0sNI" sgloss="prayer" stem="ayamihâwin" suffix="0">ayamihâwin</w>
.</q>
<gloss>“So now long shall you live, brothers, now you have accepted this faith.”</gloss>
</seg>
</p>

<p n="29">

<seg n="29.1">
<w canon="tâpiskôc" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="like" stem="tâpiskôc">tâpiskôc</w>
<w canon="ayamihêwiyiniw" class="na" gcat="3sNA" sgloss="priest" stem="ayamihêwiyiniw" suffix="0">ayamihêwiyiniw</w>
<w canon="wîsahkêcâhk" class="na" gcat="3sNA" sgloss="Wisahketchahk" stem="wîsahkêcâhkw" suffix="0">wîsahkêcâhk</w>
,
<w canon="ê-miyât" class="vta" gcat="3s3oTAcnj" preverbs="ê|cnj" sgloss="give_to" stem="miy" suffix="-ât">êh-miyât</w>
<w canon="mahîhkana" class="na" gcat="3oNA" sgloss="wolf" stem="mahîhkan" suffix="-a">mahîhkanah</w>
<w canon="ayamihâwin" class="ni" gcat="0sNI" sgloss="prayer" stem="ayamihâwin" suffix="0">ayamihâwin</w>
.
<gloss>Just like a priest was Wisahketchahk, as he gave religious instruction to the wolves.</gloss>
</seg>

<seg n="29.2">
<w canon="kîtahtawê" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="at_times" stem="kêtahtawê">kîtahtawêh</w>
<w canon="ê-apit" class="vai" gcat="3sAIcnj" preverbs="ê|cnj" sgloss="sit" stem="api" suffix="-t">êh-apit</w>
<w canon="mêkwâc" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="while" stem="mêkwâc">mêkwâc</w>
<w canon="wîsahkêcâhk" class="na" gcat="3sNA" sgloss="Wisahketchahk" stem="wîsahkêcâhkw" suffix="0">wîsahkêcâhk</w>
,
<w canon="kahkiyaw" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="every" stem="kahkiyaw">kahkiyaw</w>
<w canon="kwâskwêpayihoyiwa" class="vai" gcat="3oAI" sgloss="leap_up" stem="kwâskwêpayiho" suffix="-yiwa">kwâskwêpayihoyiwa</w>
<w canon="mahîhkana" class="na" gcat="3oNA" sgloss="wolf" stem="mahîhkan" suffix="-a">mahîhkanah</w>
,
<w canon="ê-pahkisiniyit" class="vai" gcat="3oAIcnj" preverbs="ê|cnj" sgloss="fall" stem="pahkisin" suffix="-yit">êh-pahkisiniyit</w>
,
<w canon="ê-piscipoyit" class="vai" gcat="3oAIcnj" preverbs="ê|cnj" sgloss="be_poisoned" stem="pihcipo" suffix="-yit">êh-piscipoyit</w>
,
<w canon="kahkiyaw" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="every" stem="kahkiyaw">kahkiyaw</w>
<w canon="ê-nipiyit" class="vai" gcat="3oAIcnj" preverbs="ê|cnj" sgloss="die" stem="nipi" suffix="-yit">êh-nipiyit</w>
.
<gloss>Presently, as Wisahketchahk sat there, all the wolves leaped up in the air and fell down, poisoned, and they all died.</gloss>
</seg>
</p>

<p n="30">

<seg n="30.1">
<q rend="PRE 1 POST0">
<w canon="maci-kakêpâtisak" class="na" gcat="3pNA" prenouns="maci|bad" sgloss="stupid_person" stem="kakêpâtis" suffix="-ak">maci-kakêpâtisak</w>
<w canon="ôki" class="dem" gcat="3pDEM" sgloss="this" stem="awa" suffix="-3p">ôki</w>
!</q>
<gloss>“These stupid fools!</gloss>
</seg>

<seg n="30.2">
<q rend="PRE 0 POST1">
<w canon="nika-ôh-ta-tipahikâkêwâh" class="vai" gcat="1sAIhrel" prefix="1" preverbs="ka|will ôh|thence dupL|L.REDUP" sgloss="pay_people" stem="tipahikâkê" suffix="-wâh">nik-ôh-ta-tipahikâkêwâ</w>
!</q>
<w canon="itêw" class="vta" gcat="3s3oTA" sgloss="say_to" stem="it" suffix="-êw">itêw</w>
<w canon="êsa" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="reportedly" stem="êsa">ês</w>
<w canon="ôhi" class="dem" gcat="3oDEM" sgloss="this" stem="awa" suffix="-3o">ôhi</w>
<w canon="mahîhkana" class="na" gcat="3oNA" sgloss="wolf" stem="mahîhkan" suffix="-a">mahîhkanah</w>
<w canon="wîsahkêcâhk" class="na" gcat="3sNA" sgloss="Wisahketchahk" stem="wîsahkêcâhkw" suffix="0">wîsahkêcâhk</w>
.
<gloss>I surely did need something to pay my debts with!” Wisahketchahk must have said to those wolves.</gloss>
<note>CHECK Weird verb form: HCW yup.  (future + hpreterite = irrealis)</note>
</seg>
</p>

<p n="31">

<seg n="31.1">
<w canon="êkwa" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="then" stem="êkwa">êkwah</w>
<w canon="wiyanihêw" class="vta" gcat="3s3oTA" sgloss="skin" stem="wiyanih" suffix="-êw">wiyinihêw</w>
,
<w canon="ê-kîwêhtahât" class="vta" gcat="3s3oTAcnj" preverbs="ê|cnj" sgloss="take_home" stem="kîwêhtah" suffix="-ât">êh-kîwêhtahât</w>
,
<w canon="êkwa" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="then" stem="êkwa">êkwah</w>
<w canon="mahkêsîsa" class="na" gcat="3oNA" sgloss="Fox" stem="mahkêsîs" suffix="-a">mahkêsîsah</w>
<w canon="mîna" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="also" stem="mîna">mînah</w>
<w canon="kahkiyaw" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="every" stem="kahkiyaw">kahkiyaw</w>
.
<gloss>Then he skinned them and took their skins home, and all the foxes' too.</gloss>
</seg>

<seg n="31.2">
<w canon="mahîhkana" class="na" gcat="3oNA" sgloss="wolf" stem="mahîhkan" suffix="-a">mahîhkanah</w>
<w canon="ayamihâwin" class="ni" gcat="0sNI" sgloss="prayer" stem="ayamihâwin" suffix="0">ayamihâwin</w>
<w canon="kâ-kiskinôhamawât" class="vta" gcat="3s3oTAcnj" preverbs="kâ|cnj" sgloss="teach" stem="kiskinahamaw" suffix="-ât">kâ-kiskinôhamawât</w>
,
<w canon="kahkiyaw" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="every" stem="kahkiyaw">kahkiyaw</w>
<w canon="nipahêw" class="vta" gcat="3s3oTA" sgloss="kill" stem="nipah" suffix="-êw">nipahêw</w>
.
<gloss>Having taught the wolves religion, he killed them all.</gloss>
</seg>

<seg n="31.3">
<w canon="êkosi" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="thus" stem="êkosi">êkosi</w>
<w canon="kahkiyaw" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="every" stem="kahkiyaw">kahkiyaw</w>
<w canon="tipaham" class="vti" gcat="3sTI" sgloss="measure" stem="tipah" suffix="-am">tipaham</w>
<w canon="omasinahikêwina" class="ni" gcat="0pNIof3s" prefix="3" sgloss="writing" stem="masinahikêwin" suffix="-a">omasinahikêwinah</w>
,
<w canon="ê-wayêsimât" class="vta" gcat="3s3oTAcnj" preverbs="ê|cnj" sgloss="trick_by_speech" stem="wayêsim" suffix="-ât">êh-wayêsimât</w>
<w canon="mahîhkana" class="na" gcat="3oNA" sgloss="wolf" stem="mahîhkan" suffix="-a">mahîhkanah</w>
.
<gloss>In this way he paid all his debts, by deceiving the wolves with talk.</gloss>
</seg>
</p>

<p n="32">

<seg n="32.1">
<w canon="êkosi" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="thus" stem="êkosi">êkosi</w>
<w canon="êkoyikohk" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="that_much" stem="êkoyikohk">êkoyikohk</w>
.
<gloss>That is all.</gloss>
</seg>
</p>
